==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|it}} ''[[seguire]]'', "to [[follow]]", from Latin ''[[sequi]]''; originally a musical term.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˈsɛgweɪ/|/ˈsɛɪgweɪ/}}
* {{audio|en-us-segue.ogg|Audio (US)}}

====Homophones====
